        <div class="col-md-6 solution_inner_container">
        <div class="solution_block">
        <h1 class="solution_title">CREATE</h1>
        <p class="solution_description">
          Below the Surface creates drilled well water systems in Ethiopia that provide communities with clean water from hard to reach aquifers. Each system has a well yield designed specifically to match the water demand peak needs of each community.
         </p>
           <!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-info btn-lg donate_button" role="button">Donate to our organization</a> -->
